                },
                {
                    "name": "Medical Service Prices",
                    "type": "section",
                    "text": "The physician and surgeon are masters of Medicine; the apothecary and plague doctor are experts. Plague doctors charge five times this rate, and surgeons 10 times. <br/><br/><b>Identify Affliction</b>: 1 sp. <br/><b>Treat Wounds</b>: 2 sp. <br/><b>Treat Disease</b>: 1 gp. <br/><b>First Aid or Treating a Poison</b>: 1 sp.",
